des:
Voice control your domestic appliances using Zoook Smart app and make them smart. This skill will work with Zoook Clicker (IR blaster), 10amp smart-plug, 16amp smart plug, Zoook Shine (Smart wifi bulb). It can be used to voice control your TV, heater, Mosquito repellent, set-top box, lights, fans, coffee machine, AC etc. Please use Zoook Smart app (ios or android) to configure your Zoook devices to your home wifi network and give them distinct awesome names. 

After connecting Alexa to your Zoook Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our " Zoook Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one account in our "Zoook Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some Zoook Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " Zoook Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Zoook Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Zoook Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Zoook Smart", and you'll be navigated toZoook Smart login page;
(9). Input your Zoook Smart account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these: 
 "Alexa, Turn on TV 
 "Alexa, Turn on Air Conditioner" 
 "Alexa, Turn on Geyser" 
 "Alexa, Turn off Lamp" 
 "Alexa, Set temperature to 24 on AC"
